  <brief_title>A Study to Establish the Safety and Tolerability of Zimura® (Anti-C5 Aptamer) in Combination With Anti-VEGF Therapy in Subjects With Idiopathic Polypoidal Choroidal Vasculopathy (IPCV)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2a Study to Establish the Safety and Tolerability of Zimura® (Anti-C5 Aptamer) in Combination With Anti-VEGF Therapy in Subjects With Idiopathic Polypoidal Choroidal Vasculopathy (IPCV)</official_title>
