  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objectives of this study are to evaluate the safety and tolerability of Zimura®
      intravitreous injection in combination with anti-VEGF therapy in subjects with Idiopathic
      Polypoidal Choroidal Vasculopathy (IPCV).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Treatment experienced (Prior treatment with anti-VEGF monotherapy of ≥8 injections in the
      previous twelve (12) months) subjects with IPCV will receive 3 monthly (Q4W) injections of
      Zimura® in combination with anti-VEGF therapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
